The docstring says: "Features without a scope field are allowed for all scopes."

But the code calls `config.scope.includes(scope)` without checking if `config.scope` is defined. This will throw a `TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'includes')` when a feature has no `scope` field.

The fix should be:
```typescript
